    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>Welcome To Extinction</u></strong></h2>After the failure of project 1306, you as the sole survivor must fight against the mutant insects before they can reach earth.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073790/extras/29f8b4c270c991225d5a8ef909faa918.poster.avif?t=1759330615\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073790/extras/29f8b4c270c991225d5a8ef909faa918.webm?t=1759330615\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073790/extras/29f8b4c270c991225d5a8ef909faa918.mp4?t=1759330615\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>Dash In And Out of Danger</u></strong></h2>Another part of your fighting style is how to use your dash. One of our most pivotal mechanics is our dash, moving in and out of fights at speeds whith some invincibility. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073790/extras/2b7ad9582ef4d12497773f61abf047cf.poster.avif?t=1759330615\" width=512 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073790/extras/2b7ad9582ef4d12497773f61abf047cf.webm?t=1759330615\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073790/extras/2b7ad9582ef4d12497773f61abf047cf.mp4?t=1759330615\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>Fight With Your Own Style</u></strong></h2>With multiple guns to chose from you can have your own way of fighting. Be it the standard pistol, maybe picking up a second one, blowing through insects brains with a shotgun, or witling their health down with a SMG. Even some special harder to get ones like a rocket launcher or a sniper rifle. Many ways to cut through their numbers.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073790/extras/b70401d7a652fd9441b5951bd6f19938.poster.avif?t=1759330615\" width=512 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073790/extras/b70401d7a652fd9441b5951bd6f19938.webm?t=1759330615\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073790/extras/b70401d7a652fd9441b5951bd6f19938.mp4?t=1759330615\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>Upgrade And Improve</u></strong></h2>Through out the lab you will find some upgrades to your stats and equipment. These are important, needed to fight off the harder and harder bugs as you fight deeper into the lab.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>Fight Bigger and Bigger Creatures</u></strong></h2>Speaking of going deeper, further in the insects get harder to fight, and some bigger and stronger bugs come out to end your expedition. You can even run into colony leaders, the biggest and baddest of a species, whipping them out may lead to their extinction<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073790/extras/53f5fd75b9e76c1a59429a1eafb75c0f.poster.avif?t=1759330615\" width=512 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073790/extras/53f5fd75b9e76c1a59429a1eafb75c0f.webm?t=1759330615\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073790/extras/53f5fd75b9e76c1a59429a1eafb75c0f.mp4?t=1759330615\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>Explore Deeper Into The Lab</u></strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073790/extras/efc2f062ca6eca78916bf2ffb60dddc9.poster.avif?t=1759330615\" width=512 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073790/extras/efc2f062ca6eca78916bf2ffb60dddc9.webm?t=1759330615\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073790/extras/efc2f062ca6eca78916bf2ffb60dddc9.mp4?t=1759330615\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
